description:
This is a 20 minute workout called '20 Min INTERMEDIATE CALISTHENICS WORKOUT at Home | No Equipment' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow Along with this no equipment full body intermediate Calisthenics workout you can do at home. The 20 minute workout includes the best intermediate Calisthenics exercises for building strength, skill and mobility. Include this in your Calisthenics training for enhanced results.
